{"lemma":"أَسْوَأُ","slug":"أَسْوَأُ","root":"س.#.#","root_slug":"س-_-_","root_link":"/words/roots/س-_-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"أَسْوَأ","root":"سوأ","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":8},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n21135"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%B3%D9%92%D9%88%D9%8E%D8%A3%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"elative degree of سَيِّئ (sayyiʔ):; worse, eviler; worst, evilest"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"elative degree of سَيِّئ (sayyiʔ):; more abominable; most abominable"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"elative degree of سَيِّئ (sayyiʔ):; fouler; foulest"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"elative degree of سَيِّئ (sayyiʔ):; unseemlier, unsightlier, uglier; unseemliest, unsightliest, ugliest"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"bad, evil"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"abominable"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"foul"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"unseemly, unsightly, ugly"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Elative of سَيِّئ (sayyiʔ, “bad, evil; abominable; foul; unseemly”).\n\nColor or defect adjective from the root س و ء (s w ʔ)."},"ipa":["/ʔas.waʔ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n21135","headword_ar":"اَسْوَاُ","root":"swA^","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"; fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwo'aY","text_ar":"سُوْءَى"},{"kind":"text","text":": see the latter word. One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa A^asowaA^u Alqawomi","text_ar":"هُوَ اَسْوَاُ القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is the most evil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqobaHuhumo","text_ar":"اَقْبَحُهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hiYa Als~uwo'aY","text_ar":"هِىَ السُّوْءَى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She is the most evil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (Msb.) And the [common] people say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asowaA^u AlA^aHowaAli","text_ar":"اَسْوَاُ الاَحْوَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"worst,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most scanty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weakest, of states"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conditions."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)       -A2-  [Also,] applied as an epithet to a man, (El-Umawee, M, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Evil, bad, abominable, foul, unseemly, unsightly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ugly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ElUmawee, M, K, TA:) fem. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sawoA='u","text_ar":"سَوْا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (El-Umawee, M, K,) which is thus applied to a woman; (ElUmawee, S, M;) or this is an instance of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEElaA='u","text_ar":"فَععلَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"having no [masc. of the measure]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afaEalu","text_ar":"اَفَعَلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, TA.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sawo'apN","text_ar":"سَوْءَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places. It is said in a trad. (M, TA) of the Prophet, or of 'Omar, (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waluwdN xayorN mino HasonaA='a EaqiymK","text_ar":"وَلُودٌ خَيْرٌ مِنْ حَسْنَا=ءَ عَقِيمٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sawoA='u","text_ar":"سَوْا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An ugly prolific woman is better than a beautiful barren one"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["M","TA"]}]}}